net.nightwhistler.htmlspanner.style

Class Style

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.nightwhistler.htmlspanner.style.Style

  • public class Style
extends java.lang.Object
    CSS Style object. A Style is immutable: using a setter creates a new Style object with the changed setings.
